reviewText: good, if weird flick, definitely worth a watch.

One of my favorite movie in an amazing steelbook, what's not to like? Well I'm not a fan of the blu Ray band, but other than that, it's great and would recommend to any of my friends, if there are any left!
Great product! One thing to keep in mind is that the blue "Blu-Ray" bar on the top is not paper or a sticker, it is actually part of the steelbook finish.
steelbook damaged with a large dint very disappointed,in all the steelbooks I have purchased this is the only one damaged.
